'''第51屆[[坎城影展|坎城影展]]'''於1998年5月13日至5月24日在[[法國|法國]][[坎城|坎城]]舉辦<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=986&s=Features|title=CANNES '98:WHAT'S IN THE CANNES|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2013-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907162933/http://urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=986&s=Features|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=1095&s=Features|title=CANNES 1998 – THE FESTIVAL FILMS|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2013-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907182254/http://urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=1095&s=Features|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，開幕片為美國導演[[迈克·尼科尔斯|麥克·尼可斯]]執導的《[[這個總統真太濫|風起雲湧]]》，閉幕片則是德國導演[[羅蘭·艾默瑞奇|羅倫·艾默里奇]]執導的科幻片《[[酷斯拉|酷斯拉]]》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/1998_cannes_film_festival_lineup|title=1998 Cannes Film Festival Lineup|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414022140/http://www.indiewire.com/article/1998_cannes_film_festival_lineup|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://variety.com/1998/more/news/cannes-opens-quietly-1117470796/| title=Cannes opens quietly| accessdate=10 December 2013| work=Variety| archive-date=2020-02-17| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200217144945/https://variety.com/1998/more/news/cannes-opens-quietly-1117470796/| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/may/13/entertainment/ca-49080|title=Year of the Bigfoot : 'Godzilla' is just the biggest example of the strong American presence--from movies even to the jury president--at the 51st Festival International du Film.|accessdate=10 December 2013|work=Los Angeles Times|first=Kenneth|last=Turan|date=13 May 1998|archive-date=2013-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218124935/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/may/13/entertainment/ca-49080|dead-url=no}}</ref>，最高榮譽[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]則頒給了希臘導演[[泰奧·安哲羅普洛斯|泰奧·安哲羅普洛斯]]執導的《[[永恒与一天|永遠的一天]]》。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/archives/1998/allAward.html|title=Awards 1998 : All Awards|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506030453/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/archives/1998/allAward.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=1148&s=Features|title=CANNES 1998: NEWS (2)|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2013-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130907173822/http://urbancinefile.com.au/home/view.asp?a=1148&s=Features|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

